(VERSION 1.3) (09-08-02)

CS_Motel_TWS, a map by The Wormhole Studios

You can download the suburban houses as prefabs here: http://www.fpsbanana.com/prefabs/3868

------------
INSTALL
------------

1. Put the files "CS_Motel_TWS.bsp" & "CS_Motel_TWS.nav" & "CS_Motel_TWS.txt" here:
"C:\Programs\Steam\SteamApps\1245780\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps"

2. Start up Counter-Strike: Source and play CS_Motel_TWS !
